'''斐濟美人魚'''是一具由風乾的幼猴上半身與魚下半身縫合而成的木乃伊偽標本。魚鱗上黏有動物毛，胸部長著下垂乳房，並做出張嘴露牙，右手緊貼右臉頰，左手撐著下巴的動作。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=P. T. Barnum and the Feejee Mermaid|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/1498966?origin=crossref|last=Levi|first=Steven C.|date=1977-04|journal=Western Folklore|issue=2|doi=10.2307/1498966|volume=36|pages=149|access-date=2021-08-31|archive-date=2021-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210901021045/https://www.jstor.org/stable/1498966?origin=crossref|dead-url=no}}</ref>它是[[美國|美國]][[馬戲團|馬戲團]]開創者[[費尼爾司·泰勒·巴納姆|P.T.巴納姆]]的眾多騙局之一，他向觀眾謊稱該美人魚是在南太平洋[[斐濟|斐濟]]附近海域捕獲的。<ref name="Boese, Alex 2014">Boese, Alex (2014). "The Feejee Mermaid."</ref>

1842年，巴納姆曾在[[紐約|紐約]]{{tsl|en|Barnum's American Museum|巴納姆美國珍奇博館}}展出斐濟美人魚原件，其後也製作許多複製品與變體，以相同的名義展出。<ref>{{cite book|last=Nickell|first=Joe|title=Secrets of the Sideshows|url=https://archive.org/details/secretssideshows00nick|year=2005|publisher=University Press of Kentucky|location=Lexington|pages=[https://archive.org/details/secretssideshows00nick/page/n355 333]–335}}</ref>然而原件現已佚失，很可能與巴納姆的其他收藏一樣毀於火災。<ref name="Levi, Steven C 1977">Levi, Steven C (April 1977). "P. T. Barnum and the Feejee Mermaid". Western Folklore 36 (2): 149.</ref>

